{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act19side", "eventName": "綠野幻夢", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DV-4", "avgTag": "行動後", "storyName": "無人的小巷", "storyInfo": "城中，塞雷婭正要將動力甲徹底擊潰，千鈞一髮之際，博士出聲阻止，從動力甲中救出了繆爾賽思；城外，一行人終於進入多蘿西的實驗室，拓荒者們卻第一時間將弓弩對準多蘿西。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "黑色填滿了整個狹小的空間，隔絕了光線、空氣與聲響。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "想用嘴呼喊。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "源石引擎運作帶來的高溫塞住了喉管，沒有聲音能發出來。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "想用手敲打。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "堅硬的鋼鐵緊緊壓住了四肢，連躲閃的餘地都沒有，談何反抗。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "要是能落下眼淚就好了。從小媽媽就說，淚水是很好的武器。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "可是眼睛不願意。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "數百年來，它們看過太多崩塌的山和乾涸的水，也見證了太多親人的消逝。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 800.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "它們變得越來越乾燥，就像移動城市碾過的土地。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g8_alley_n", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第六具動力甲，確認癱瘓。", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些就是全部？", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來是這樣。他們成功拖住了我們十三分鐘。", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等——", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "掃描結果顯示，還有第七具！", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_mechawalk"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_526_1#1$1", "fadetime": 2.5}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "奇怪的動力甲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_526_1#1$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_526_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_mecharun"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 300.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.1}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士小心！它往你的方向去了！", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 51, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_526_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.8}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "奇怪的動力甲"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "xpos": 100.0, "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.61}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_526_1#1$1", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.51, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_526_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_532_1#4$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_526_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_532_1#4$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我來。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#4$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_526_1#1$1", "name2": "avg_npc_532_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.51, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.8, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.52}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你看不清塞雷婭是怎麼移動的，在你的雙腿反應過來之前，她已經站在了你的面前。"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你知道，在哥倫比亞的街道上，她從來不會帶上那面萊茵製造的盾牌。"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她會把自己變成盾。"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從她交疊的小臂上，琺瑯質迅速生長開，替你擋下了動力甲的一擊。"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "害蟲。", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#8$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "Characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.4}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.1}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽到塞雷婭低聲說。"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她一直這麼看待這些失控的哥倫比亞技術。"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從她的表情與姿態中，你讀出了她下一步的動作。"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在準備消滅害蟲的時候，塞雷婭從來不會浪費時間。"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的手即將觸到動力甲的前胸，那裡很快就會出現一個黑漆漆的空洞——"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "面前這具動力甲會被摧毀，或者說，“死去”。"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一個念頭在你的腦子裡躥了上來。"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "MusicVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.1, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "停下，塞雷婭！", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line101"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞雷婭也許只聽到了你喊出來的第一個音節，但她的確收了手。"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是你們長期並肩作戰累積下來的信任。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$e_atk_circleatk_h"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.1}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她的拳頭錯開了核心，可攻擊的餘波依舊震碎了動力甲的上半截外殼。"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從無數飛濺的金屬碎片中，你看到了一抹亮色。"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就像......髮絲。"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，危險！別靠近——", "name": "Mechanist"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_521_1#1$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_532_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是......", "name": "塞雷婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_532_1#5$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "29_i02", "xScale": 1.5, "yScale": 1.5, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 0.8, "yScaleTo": 0.8, "duration": 40.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動力甲正在倒下。"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更多碎片飛了出來，很快，你看到了更多髮絲，一點皮膚，然後是一隻眼睛。"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那隻眼睛看向了你。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "憤怒，驚恐，迷茫......你在一瞬間讀出了很多情緒。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在所有情緒隨著偽裝的外殼一起剝落之後，你發現它在向你求救。"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "於是，你伸出了一隻手。"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你好，繆爾賽思。", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line140"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g4_corridor", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$nervous_intro", "key": "$nervous_loop", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁爾，這是怎麼回事？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不知道......我不知道，領隊......", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你先放開摩爾醫生。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫生......", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不能放開她。", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不聽我的命令？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領隊，你為什麼還跟她們站在一起？", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是說，我們必須狠下心來對她們下手嗎？你不是說......我們只是她們豢養的實驗動物嗎？", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是你勸我跟你一塊幹的。我本來......我很喜歡摩爾醫生。", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......沒想到，最先站出來反對我的人會是你。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我甚至想過會是薩姆，或者其他人......邁爾，你從來都最聽我的話。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也說過，我太聽話了。", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前我聽老闆的，在工廠裡得了礦石病......來了這裡，我就聽你的。", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們都是有本事的人，聰明，讀書多。我覺得聽你們的不會錯。", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但現在......我們都要死了。", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼，我們都快被這幾個做研究的人害死了！她們還覺得自己能控制一切！", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不信的話，你搜一下她，她身上一定有錄音用的機器，她這一路上跟著我們就是為了觀察我們，也觀察那些銀色的怪物！", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......烏比卡博士，要是有脫困的方法，你該開口了。", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "奧利維亞，我的確沒有把實驗資訊告訴你......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我絕對不會騙你。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼，邁爾，我也沒有騙過你們。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#9$1"}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......真的不知道對付它們的方法。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我記錄它們的資料，研究它們，都是因為我也想解決眼前的問題......我說過了，這是我工作的一部分。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#8$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#6$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁爾先生，我想埃琳娜沒有撒謊。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你能把喬伊絲還給我們了嗎？", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈......哈哈哈......", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拓荒者盯著白面鴞，突然抬手。"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一聲叫喊凝在了赫默嗓子眼，無人機接收到了主人的意志，狠狠撞向拓荒者的身體。"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可他只是從白面鴞手上取下了一樣東西。"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那是他在幾個小時前親手給她戴上的緊急醫療環。"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_128_plosis_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "白面鴞"}, "figure_art": "avg_128_plosis_1#8$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我都幹了些什麼啊？", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "摩爾醫生......", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你會怪我嗎？你會不會後悔曾經對我那麼好？", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我這樣的人......根本不配被你拯救。", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫生回到了她的朋友們身邊。她依然安靜，美麗，無瑕。"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是所有人都無處可逃了。這座實驗室就是一個為他們提前準備好的墓穴。"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有人能得救，這該死的環只是那該死的公司給他們套上的鐐銬。"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們都得不到自由，除非......"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拓荒者突然把緊急醫療環整個塞進了嘴裡。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "邁爾！", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "領、領隊......", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在幹什麼？快吐出來！", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 227, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這醫療環......", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#5$1"}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "裡面還剩大量止痛劑。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#7$1"}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一口氣吞掉這麼多，心臟根本受不了，他會休克的！", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#6$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我見過......有人偷偷地把這個吞下去......", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 235, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們都死了！", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那他們很......幸運。", "name": "拓荒隊成員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_534_1#1$1"}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "該死，你給我吐出來！", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 241, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我按住他的嘴，薩姆，你給我揍他肚子！", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Dialog", "attribu