#10$1"}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......確實。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很意外。你並不知道喬伊絲身上發生了什麼。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#3$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這說明情況早就脫離了你的控制。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#3$1"}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜，關於這項實驗......你真的該開口了。", "name": "赫默"}, "figure_art": "avg_108_silent_1#10$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道多蘿西真的......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#12$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論如何，我都不想看到任何人因為這個實驗受傷，尤其是喬伊絲。", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許你是對的，我們本該一起解決這個問題......", "name": "埃琳娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_135_halo_1#3$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，埃琳娜，不必再猶豫了。", "name": "溫柔的女聲"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是我邀請大家到這裡來的，無論是赫默醫生還是我的拓荒者朋友們，大家都有權知道真相。", "name": "溫柔的女聲"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你一直在......監控我們？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很擔心你們。", "name": "溫柔的女聲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你們停下腳步說話的時候，需要有人替你們關上門......", "name": "溫柔的女聲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你擋住了那些銀色怪物？", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "桑尼，請不要這麼稱呼他們。", "name": "溫柔的女聲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們能聽見。", "name": "溫柔的女聲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#7$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "桑尼"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_535_1#11$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃琳娜，親愛的助手，我要再拜託你一件事。", "name": "溫柔的女聲"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請把大家帶來見我。", "name": "溫柔的女聲"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不方便解釋的事情，我可以解釋。", "name": "溫柔的女聲"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且......你很清楚，我的實驗室是最安全的。", "name": "溫柔的女聲"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "29_g3_cottage", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1